13.84	The_Last_Ninja	The Last Ninja	The Last Ninja is an action-adventure game developed and published by System 3 in 1987 for the Commodore 64. As the first in the Last Ninja series, it set the standard for the unique look and feel for its sequels: Last Ninja 2 , Last Ninja Remix (1990, a remake of the first game on Amiga and remake of the second game on Commodore 64) and Last Ninja 3 (1991).	http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/thumb/d/d3/LastNinja-c64_cover01.jpg/250px-LastNinja-c64_cover01.jpg
